eelah was a dancer at the Moonstone Mask.
She had aspirations to study dance at the conservatory in Waterdeep, but lacked the money to pay for it. Until then, she worked for Ophala Cheldarstorn. If the Kalach-Cha came with Elanee, Teelah and Elanne would make some agressive comments. The Kalach-Cha couldve stood with Elanee to gain influence with her.
